INSERT INTO exercises (name, difficulty, tips, link) VALUES ('Shoulders Stretch Variation One', 0, 'Reach one arm behind your body, with your elbow pointing upward behind your head. Assist the stretch with your other hand on your elbow to engage your shoulder. Pause for a few seconds, then repeat the stretch with your other arm. ', 'https://youtu.be/UFCLH__899A');
